# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for Node.js v0.8.4 (http://nodejs.org)
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * Mario Fernandez (https://github.com/sirech)
#  * Nicholas Penree (https://github.com/drudge)
#
